  "title": "Peranakan Service & Cuisine Crew Leader",
  "description": "<p><strong>About Us</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>At The Peranakan Group, food is more than just a meal — it is <strong>heritage, community, and connection</strong>. From classic dishes like Laksa and Ayam Buah Keluak to festive Tok Panjang feasts, we celebrate the richness of Peranakan culture through authentic cuisine and heartfelt service.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are expanding our team and looking for passionate individuals to join us as <strong>Service &amp; Cuisine Preparation Staff</strong>, where you’ll play an important role in creating memorable dining experiences for our guests.</p>\n<h2>Responsibilities</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist in <strong>preparing traditional Peranakan dishes</strong>, including kueh, sambal, curries, and daily specials.</li>\n  <li>Support chefs with ingredient preparation (chopping, marinating, plating, etc.).</li>\n  <li>Provide excellent <strong>customer service</strong> in both dine-in and takeaway settings.</li>\n  <li>Uphold food safety and hygiene standards in line with SFA requirements.</li>\n  <li>Assist with festive events and Tok Panjang banquets.</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness and organisation of kitchen and service areas.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Requirements</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Interest in <strong>Peranakan cuisine and culture</strong> (training will be provided).</li>\n  <li>Basic kitchen or F&amp;B service experience preferred, but not required.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work in a <strong>fast-paced environment</strong> while paying attention to detail.</li>\n  <li>Team player with a positive, service-oriented attitude.</li>\n  <li>Flexibility to work on weekends and public holidays.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>What We Offer</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Competitive salary package with meal allowance.</li>\n  <li>On-the-job training in <strong>Peranakan cooking and service skills</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Career development opportunities within our growing F&amp;B group.</li>\n  <li>A supportive, community-driven workplace.</li>\n  <li>Staff meals and staff discounts at our outlets.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>How to Apply</h2>\n<p>If you have a passion for heritage, hospitality, and food that tells a story, join us in keeping the <strong>Peranakan legacy alive</strong>!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>📧 Email your CV to: <strong>christiekhoo@solutions17.com</strong><br>\n📞 Contact us at: <strong>94761688</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>",
